description._content: Title: Les Travaux Publics de la France, Tome Cinquieme: Phares et Balises [Title Page] Alternative Title: Public Works of France, Fifth Volume: Lighthouses and Beacons [Title Page] Creator: Allard, E. Date: 1883 Series: Tome Cinquieme: Phares et Balises Place: France Description: The full title of the five-volume set is, Les travaux publics de la France par MM. F. Lucas et V. Fournie - Ed. Collignon - H. de Lagrene - Voisin Bey - E. Allard. Ouvrage publie sous les auspices de Ministere des travaux publics et sous la direction de M. Leonce Reynaud. This is the title page of Public Works of France, Volume Five: Lighthouses and Beacons.
